text.tspan: Some problems give us two equations each of which has two variables

text.tspan: For example if 3x + y = 10 , y = x -2 what is the value of y ?

text.style: -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); text-anchor: middle; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; cursor: pointer;
text.tspan: One method to solve this type of question is SUBSTITUTION , in SUBSTITUTION we insert the expression
for one variable in one equation into that variable in the other equation
